{"tid":1959403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度女醫生到民居檢查遇襲　最大貧民窟首現確診","createTime":"2020-04-05T11:11:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T09:33:33.000Z","uid":133680,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1016c98ba4b642a66373afe3f2bf3d4b46dbe586","tid":1959403,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T11:11:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/456333/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E5%88%B0%E6%B0%91%E5%B1%85%E6%AA%A2%E6%9F%A5%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E8%B2%A7%E6%B0%91%E7%AA%9F%E9%A6%96%E7%8F%BE%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F456333%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%259F%25A5%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%25A5%25B2-%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25B2%25A7%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25AA%259F%25E9%25A6%2596%25E7%258F%25BE%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA&d=4DrNtUYtvprXc3sGeUgfz4eonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=33542946\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/456333/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E5%88%B0%E6%B0%91%E5%B1%85%E6%AA%A2%E6%9F%A5%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E8%B2%A7%E6%B0%91%E7%AA%9F%E9%A6%96%E7%8F%BE%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA</a><br />\n印度的新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情（COVID-19）逐漸惡化，確診病例呈快速上升趨勢。位於孟買（Mumbai）的最大貧民窟塔拉維（Dharavi）4月1日出現首宗確診病例。另外有醫護人員到民居檢查時遭到襲擊，7名疑犯4月2日被捕。<br />\n<br />\n印度衛生部官網最新數據顯示，截至當地時間4月2日下午6時，確診病例達到2,069宗，其中53人死亡，156人治癒出院。塔拉維貧民窟4月1日一名56歲男子確診，當晚病情惡化，轉院期間病逝。<br />\n<br />\n新德里回教傳道會3月舉辦大型宗教聚會，目前相關確診個案達300宗，已有10人死亡，為印度目前最大的感染群。政府正在追蹤9,000名曾出席聚會的信徒，但仍然未掌握他們的下落。一名不願意具名的印度衛生部門高層官員表示，懷疑病毒是由參與聚會的外國人傳入印度。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYennefer ❤❤<br />\n@Poorvaholics<br />\nI don't want to spoil your morning but this is what happening in #indore. people attacking doctors who is visiting them for sample collection 😟 god bless us and doctors<br />\n<br />\nEmbedded video<br />\n219<br />\n11:55 AM - Apr 2, 2020<br />\nTwitter Ads info and privacy<br />\n132 people are talking about this<br />\n<br />\n印度中央邦印多爾市（Indore）多名醫護人員4月1日遭居民襲擊，兩名女醫生受傷。其中一名醫生指，過去三日前往當地進行檢查，並得悉有老婦曾與患者接觸，當他們與老婦交談時，突然有居民開始施襲。有人向他們擲石，最終要由警方救出。<br />\n<br />\n海得拉巴（Hyderabad）等地也出現類似情況。市民呼籲政府嚴懲施襲者，並加強保護醫護人員。總理莫迪（Narendra Modi）表示，民眾應配合醫務人員的相關工作，並強調警方將對施襲者採取嚴厲的懲罰措施。"},{"pid":"f779357212585f9819df71851b00ce28b36613f5","tid":1959403,"uid":93921,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T11:12:30.000Z","msg":"佢地家居隔離個人口密度仲高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a8b2e857ca94aaa447b00ea7ce9b280b3c8b0db","tid":1959403,"uid":51469,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T11:13:25.000Z","msg":"好彩冇強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952a4c70735e757db0be0a38827e7aa6c0f4b31d","tid":1959403,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6a8b2e857ca94aaa447b00ea7ce9b280b3c8b0db","tid":1959403,"uid":51469,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T11:13:25.000Z","msg":"好彩冇強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T11:14:07.000Z","msg":"可能襲擊就係為咗強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d6c35e994a4555d4eda7516dc725ba94729b08","tid":1959403,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"952a4c70735e757db0be0a38827e7aa6c0f4b31d","tid":1959403,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6a8b2e857ca94aaa447b00ea7ce9b280b3c8b0db","tid":1959403,"uid":51469,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T11:13:25.000Z","msg":"好彩冇強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"c